Package: waratah
Title: Easy data viz - NSW Government colour & typography design
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zoe", "Baldwin", , "zoe.baldwin@health.nsw.gov.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6010-9361"))
Description: This package allows NSW Government R users to create data visualisations in keeping with the NSW Design System. This ensures a consistent approach to data visualisations with appropriate colours and fonts. Special thanks to Carl Suster (ORCID = 0000-0001-7021-9380, Western Sydney Local Health District, NSW Health [cph]) for methodical review and feedback. This package was inspired by the data viz work of Cara Thompson https://github.com/cararthompson.
